description: Spectacular condo at the corner Columbia Road and O Street.  Directly across the street from the beach with amazing water views from every window in the unit including two private out door decks.  This unique 3 bedroom unit has many original features including, gorgeous hardwood floors throughout, pocket doors, classical architectural features and tremendous natural light. Renovated kitchen is great for entertaining.  Updated bathrooms and electrical  service, Central Air, plenty of storage, laundry room, garage parking with additional spot in the driveway.
